      • selectOneCalendar

        private java.util.Optional<java.lang.String> selectOneCalendar(java.lang.String prompt)
        display a ChoiceDialog to the user for selecting one of the existing calendars
        Parameters:
        prompt - the prompt which will be shown to the user
        Returns:
        an optional string. If present, then the user selected the calendar named by that string. If not present, then the user did not select anything (i.e. canceled)

      • getNewCalendarName

        private java.util.Optional<java.lang.String> getNewCalendarName(java.lang.String prompt)
        display a TextInputDialog to the user for naming a calendar. Validates that a calendar by the given name does not already exist.
        Parameters:
        prompt - a prompt to display to the user
        Returns:
        an optional string containing the user's input. If not present, then the user canceled the operation.
